eopatra's paramour to the letters of the alphabet. Completing the Collected Works of Velimir Khlebnikov, Selected Poems gives us insight into the imagination of a remarkable artist.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aEnglische Literatur Amerikas. 0aLyrik. 4aKhlebnikov, Velimir, 1885-1922 -- Correspondence. 4aKhlebnikov, Velimir, 1885-1922 -- Translations into English. 4aLITERARY CRITICISM / Poetry. 4aLITERARY CRITICISM / Russian & Former Soviet Union. 4aPoets, Russian -- 20th century -- Correspondence. 7aLITERARY COLLECTIONS / General.2bisacsh1 aSchmidt, Paul.1 aVroon, Ronald, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aVroon, Ronald, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertHUP e-dition: Complete eBook Packagez9783110353488oZDB-23-HCO08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertHUP e-dition: Literature eBook Packagez9783110353501oZDB-23-HLI08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertHUP eBook Package Archive 1893-1999z97831104422120 cprintz978067449795540uhttps://doi.org/10.4159/harvard.978067449796240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780674497962423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780674497962/original  a978-3-11-044221-2  HUP eBook Package Archive 1893-1999c1893d1999  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LT  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-HCO  aZDB-23-HLI